        "decision": "Promoted from preliminary intake INTAKE-GAP-011 to an active Horizon candidate; static HOR ID tracked through GitHub issue #305. Promotion does not establish a defect or admit a proposal.",
        "integrated_into": "Provisionally A-15; duplicate and scope review with APPT-004, HOR-026, and foreign-policy and authorization proposals.",
        "rationale": "Congress delegated designation authority in 22 U.S.C. § 288, the President has broad foreign-affairs authority, and the 2026 order may be an intended statutory application. One episode may not establish recurrence or difficult-to-repair institutional harm.",
        "follow_up": "Review IOIA authority, congressional participation, funding, governance, attached privileges, recurrence, review, and remedy fit before admission, merger, or rejection.",
