        "",
        "## Final Disposition — Integrated July 21, 2026",
        "",
        "HOR-025 is integrated into **REG-002 — Executive Influence over Federal Regulatory Enforcement**. It does not remain a separate candidate.",
        "",
        "The HPE–Juniper record and two private Paramount–Warner matters support development of a neutral process question: whether case-specific executive intervention in noncriminal regulatory matters is adequately documented, conflict-screened, preserved with contrary professional analysis, and reviewable without eliminating lawful policy supervision. The pleadings and reported allegations do not establish corruption.",
